{"hd284d837ge6a5g4040gb7a6gd9d25abae359": ["Your longpig started squealin' yet? Cos if you're drinkin', job must be done - <i>yeah?</i>", "126e39d1-7c38-453c-888b-4cddce7f3e41", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Goblin\\ADs\\GOB_WarchiefGrumpy_AD_WithGuard.html", "808f0183-ce37-c998-2b4f-6aa13a2dfca2"], "h8c08b21dg432eg4e17g9ab5g08d65abae2e6": ["Ah, as good as, boss! Got a professional workin' on him right now.", "0f18201e-2836-4642-8a26-d0a6e1a8a8cc", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Goblin\\ADs\\GOB_WarchiefGrumpy_AD_WithGuard.html", "e48537ca-6cd3-30c0-417c-ed444ab9c071"], "h640343cagd678g4f14g92e8g446274907d35": ["That a fact? Hope so, for your sake - plenty of room next to the piggy if you're lying.", "126e39d1-7c38-453c-888b-4cddce7f3e41", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Goblin\\ADs\\GOB_WarchiefGrumpy_AD_WithGuard.html", "a4a046df-5776-79b3-4ed4-0565d78827f4"], "h2ffb1fc9g4827g4a21ga213gfea525d0d9f6": ["'Ello, mate. How's the drow treatin' ya?", "0f18201e-2836-4642-8a26-d0a6e1a8a8cc", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Goblin\\ADs\\GOB_WarchiefGrumpy_AD_WithGuard.html", "584f1b58-5ab6-50b9-2fd5-cd5f6773c90e"], "h03acc410gf429g4c5agb1c2g355cc30bee52": ["Worse than you're treatin' that bloody prisoner. ", "126e39d1-7c38-453c-888b-4cddce7f3e41", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Goblin\\ADs\\GOB_WarchiefGrumpy_AD_WithGuard.html", "909d9368-5084-caf8-96cd-4c89653bfd53"], "ha083ca28gac97g4c59ga2f1g6602c0c2050c": ["Has he talked yet?", "126e39d1-7c38-453c-888b-4cddce7f3e41", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Goblin\\ADs\\GOB_WarchiefGrumpy_AD_WithGuard.html", "a447fec5-df3b-202d-75e5-c67f7d5d94f7"], "h116f0f1cg85b3g4051g9edcg085d9a48eaa4": ["Yeah. Mostly he just says, \"stop, argh, my guts are s'posed to be on the <i>inside</i>\".", "0f18201e-2836-4642-8a26-d0a6e1a8a8cc", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Goblin\\ADs\\GOB_WarchiefGrumpy_AD_WithGuard.html", "bd9eaeb6-0feb-5e8d-a41b-270a2f84b45a"], "h8b1e183cg3e80g4149gaf27gc569aef8cd16": ["Oi - anythin' to report?", "126e39d1-7c38-453c-888b-4cddce7f3e41", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Goblin\\ADs\\GOB_WarchiefGrumpy_AD_WithGuard.html", "d057aab1-588e-cf1b-b7a3-d92dd2931352"], "h808fd904g78b6g4bfdga400ge19ee1e43c83": ["Nah. That sack of offal won't tell us nothing.", "0f18201e-2836-4642-8a26-d0a6e1a8a8cc", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Goblin\\ADs\\GOB_WarchiefGrumpy_AD_WithGuard.html", "3dcabe2e-8267-5d47-a28a-846b2e19354c"], "h096780afg0cb9g4189g949egeced603d7ce2": ["Shite. Drow's getting impatient.", "126e39d1-7c38-453c-888b-4cddce7f3e41", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Goblin\\ADs\\GOB_WarchiefGrumpy_AD_WithGuard.html", "75e26792-efe0-ce34-012f-ca768031971a"], "h40a2f5eag21b0g4babgabb1gc026cdef934e": ["Drow says if the prisoner don't talk soon, I should cut yer arms off.", "126e39d1-7c38-453c-888b-4cddce7f3e41", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Goblin\\ADs\\GOB_WarchiefGrumpy_AD_WithGuard.html", "e9d3d6d3-5819-fcbe-3483-50c421944ecb"], "h57c9bdd3g0742g428eg881bg2cf81e0d2e79": ["You <i>wouldn't</i>.", "0f18201e-2836-4642-8a26-d0a6e1a8a8cc", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Goblin\\ADs\\GOB_WarchiefGrumpy_AD_WithGuard.html", "4625c0be-6e51-5c4f-00e8-a8e1d4e88afd"], "hf0e89e2age375g43cag9076g642304c262fd": ["I would. And I'd <i>enjoy</i> it.", "126e39d1-7c38-453c-888b-4cddce7f3e41", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Goblin\\ADs\\GOB_WarchiefGrumpy_AD_WithGuard.html", "8fa815be-de95-810c-25ce-d4daea9571bf"]}